definitions.definition: ( obsolete ) A picture drawn in line only, before the colour and/or shading is applied; an outline sketch .

main_definition: ( obsolete ) A picture drawn in line only, before the colour and/or shading is applied; an outline sketch .

definitions.definition: ( obsolete , rare ) A sentence consisting of only one line , or an epigram consisting of only one verse , of poetry .

main_definition: ( obsolete , rare ) A sentence consisting of only one line , or an epigram consisting of only one verse , of poetry .

definitions.definition: A design or motif composed of one or more letters , often intertwined , used as an identifying mark of an individual or institution; the letters are usually the initials of their names.

main_definition: A design or motif composed of one or more letters , often intertwined , used as an identifying mark of an individual or institution; the letters are usually the initials of their names.
